 So, okay, this is a really interesting question.

08:03.820 --> 08:04.780
 Let's lay it out.

08:04.780 --> 08:07.900
 So bonds, almost like cards.

08:07.900 --> 08:11.980
 We say there's bonds, there is life,

08:11.980 --> 08:14.260
 there's intelligence, there's consciousness.

