 Sure, but I'm an experimentalist as well,

10:08.700 --> 10:11.380
 so one of my, I have two superpowers.

10:11.380 --> 10:14.540
 My stupidity, and I don't mean that as a,

10:14.540 --> 10:16.620
 I'm like absolutely completely witless,

