 but I was able to think of experiments in my head

10:30.580 --> 10:35.580
 I could then do in my lab or when I was a child outside

10:35.780 --> 10:37.820
 and then those experiments in my head

10:37.820 --> 10:40.020
 and then outside reinforced one another.

