 Not a fundamental force, but it is a directing force

12:14.460 --> 12:18.140
 because existence, although existence appears

12:18.140 --> 12:21.100
 to be the default, the existence of what,

12:21.100 --> 12:24.340
 why does, and we can get to this later, I think,

