 well, we make our own meaning.

3:59:19.900 --> 3:59:20.940
 I think that's fine.

3:59:20.940 --> 3:59:24.700
 But I think the universe wants to explore

3:59:24.700 --> 3:59:27.420
 every possible configuration that it's allowed us

3:59:27.420 --> 3:59:28.620
 to explore.

